    "improvements_made": "1. Added missing SUBMISSION entity and its relationships. 2. Kept many‑to‑many junction tables USER_PROJECT and CODE_PROJECT to support collaborative projects and code reuse across projects. 3. Introduced content_hash in CODE for duplicate detection and author_user_id foreign key for clearer ownership. 4. Normalized attribute naming to snake_case and added explicit foreign‑key attributes (author_user_id, owner_user_id). 5. Defined enum‑style attributes (difficulty_level, status, role, result) for better data integrity. 6. Documented unique constraints (username, email) and suggested ON DELETE CASCADE for related FK relationships. 7. Clarified relationship cardinalities and descriptions. 8. Retained all strengths of the previous comprehensive model while streamlining and making it implementation‑ready."
